com.sterlingcommerce.woodstock.callout

Interface ISCVotingResolver

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SCBasicVotingResolver, SCCountingVotingResolver

    public interface ISCVotingResolver
    This interface provides methods that need to be implemented by the application for each callout. Framework will provide two implementations for this interface. Application can choose to use the default implementations provided by platform or write their own implementations. praveen

      Validates the response of each callout implementation SCCallOutResponse and returns a Voting response SCVotingResponse which indicates whether to proceed to the next unit or reuturn back the the application code.
